descriptionHtml:
Bykea is an all in one app for transportation, delivery and payment services. Our marketplace of services and listings help move people, parcels and payments efficiently, saving time and money.

To make a booking, just follow the following steps:

Select your service type: Ride, Delivery, Payments or Shopping

See available driver partners on the map near the pickup location

Get an instant confirmation with Bykea driver partner details

Track your Bykea as it reaches you

Once your booking ends, you can pay by cash and top up your in-app wallet

Rate your driver partner!

You can avail Bykea’s exciting offers and latest happenings by following us on social media:

Facebook - https://facebook.com/bykea

Plus, you can always reach us at info@bykea.com

Download our app and try it out! We promise to save you both time and money!

title: Bykea - Bike Taxi, Delivery & Payments

creator: Bykea Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Bykea is an all in one app for transportation, delivery and payment services. Our marketplace of services and listings help move people, parcels and payments efficiently, saving time and money.

To make a booking, just follow the following steps:

Select your service type: Ride, Delivery, Payments or Shopping

See available driver partners on the map near the pickup location

Get an instant confirmation with Bykea driver partner details

Track your Bykea as it reaches you

Once your booking ends, you can pay by cash and top up your in-app wallet

Rate your driver partner!

You can avail Bykea’s exciting offers and latest happenings by following us on social media:

Facebook - https://facebook.com/bykea

Plus, you can always reach us at info@bykea.com

Download our app and try it out! We promise to save you both time and money!
